## 💼 Orders & Customization

??? question "how to order products?"
    You can purchase our products directly through [**VIEWE official website**](https://viewedisplay.com/). Alternatively, you may also place orders via our Alibaba and AliExpress stores.

??? question "Do you offer Customization Services?"
    **Yes.** We provide ODM/OEM services including:  * **PCB Redesign**: Changing board shape, adding interfaces (RS485, CAN).   * **Screen Customization**: High brightness (1000 nits+), Touch cover lens customization.  * **Minimum Order Quantity (MOQ)**: Usually >500 units depending on complexity.   * [Contact Sales](mailto:sales@viewedisplay.com) for a quote and service.

??? question "Where can I download the datasheet?"
    All datasheets, schematics, and mechanical drawings are available in our [Resource Center](../support/resource.md).

??? question "What is the warranty policy?"
    We provide a **1-year warranty** for all standard products. This covers manufacturing defects but excludes physical damage (cracked glass, broken FPC) caused by misuse.

